[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0923","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0923.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1077","title":"Apple MacOS 9 空闲锁定安全绕过漏洞","description":"MacOS 9 空闲锁定功能存在安全绕过漏洞，本地攻击者可通过物理访问目标设备，使用程序员开关或 CMD-PWR 键盘组合键触发调试器，从而绕过空闲会话的密码保护机制，禁用系统锁定并获得非授权访问权限。该漏洞影响 MacOS 9 版本，攻击者需要本地物理访问权限，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1077"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:40.407","remediation":"升级到 Apple 不再支持的 MacOS 9 已无官方补丁可用，建议迁移至现代 macOS 版本（如 macOS Sonoma）以彻底修复。临时缓解措施包括：通过 Open Firmware 密码保护禁用程序员开关和 CMD-PWR 组合键的调试器调用，并限制物理接触来防止本地绕过。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94149318124548&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/756","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1077.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1077","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1077.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1077.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1077.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j4pc-g7pq-p2h7/GHSA-j4pc-g7pq-p2h7.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/756/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_600_700.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1077.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0923.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0653","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0653.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0854","title":"Ultimate Bulletin Board 访问控制漏洞","description":"Ultimate Bulletin Board（UBB）论坛系统存在访问控制漏洞，其将包含用户敏感信息的数据文件存储在 CGI-BIN 目录下，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过 HTTP 直接请求这些文件。当 Web 服务器尝试执行该文件时若发生错误（如权限不足或格式不支持），服务器可能返回文件原始内容而非执行结果，导致攻击者获取论坛用户数据、配置信息等敏感内容。此漏洞影响 UBB 早期版本，攻击复杂度低，危害中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0854"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:11.770","remediation":"将 UBB 数据文件移出 cgi-bin 目录至 Web 不可执行目录（如 ubb/data），并设置目录权限为 644（文件）/755（目录）；升级至 UBB 5.14 及以上版本，该版本已将数据存储路径改为非 CGI 目录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&date=2000-02-22&msg=NDBBLKOPOLNKELHPDEFKIEPGCAAA.renzo.toma%40veronica.nl","http://www.ultimatebb.com/home/versions.shtml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0653.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0616","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0616.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0830","title":"SCO UnixWare Xsco 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"SCO UnixWare 7.0/7.0.1/7.1 系统中的 Xsco 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可向该命令传递超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，导致任意代码执行或以 root 权限执行恶意指令。该漏洞影响 SCO UnixWare 多个版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高危。建议用户升级至最新版本或安装厂商提供的安全补丁。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0830"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:08.813","remediation":"建议升级至 SCO UnixWare 7.1.1 及以上版本，或安装 SCO 官方提供的 xsco 补丁。如无法升级，可移除 xsco 的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/X11/xsco），限制本地普通用户以提权方式执行该命令，从而缓解本地提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0830","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19641"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0616.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0615","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0615.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0829","title":"HP Secure Web Console 弱加密漏洞","description":"HP Secure Web Console 使用弱加密算法保护通信数据，远程攻击者可通过网络嗅探或中间人攻击截获并破解加密流量，获取敏感信息或管理权限。该漏洞影响 HP 9000 系列服务器等产品，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。建议升级至修复版本或使用强加密协议替代。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0829"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:08.690","remediation":"该漏洞源于 HP Secure Web Console 使用弱加密算法，导致攻击者可窃听管理通信。建议升级至 HP-UX 11i v3 或更高版本，在 Secure Web Console 配置中禁用 SSLv2/v3 和弱密码套件，仅启用 TLSv1.2 及以上版本并配置 AES 类强加密；同时在 /etc/hosts.allow 限制 Web Console（默认 2381 端口）仅允许可信任管理网段访问，并优先使用 SSH 替代 Web Console 进行远程管理。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0829"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0615.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0605","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0605.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0827","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 跨域导航子框架欺骗漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 5.0 及后续版本默认启用了\"跨不同域的导航子框架\"选项，远程攻击者可通过构造恶意网页，诱使用户在浏览器中访问该页面，利用不同域之间框架导航权限控制的缺失实施框架欺骗攻击。攻击者可将目标网站嵌入恶意网页的子框架中，并通过跨域导航将子框架内容替换为任意恶意内容，导致用户混淆当前浏览页面的真实来源，进而可能被诱导输入敏感信息或进行其他危险操作。该漏洞影响 Internet Explorer 5.0 及后续版本，CVSS 评分 2.6，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0827"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:08.450","remediation":"lots of notes mixed in","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0827"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0605.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0024","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0024.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0354","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 与 Word 97 模板 Visual Basic 任意代码执行漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 4.x/5.x 与 Word 97 集成时存在安全漏洞。当用户通过 IE 浏览包含恶意 Word 97 模板的网页时，浏览器不会对模板中内嵌的可执行 Visual Basic 代码发出安全警告，导致攻击者可在用户 IE 客户端上下文中执行任意 VBA 程序。该漏洞也影响 Microsoft Outlook 客户端，当用户预览或打开包含恶意 Word 模板附件的邮件时同样会触发。攻击者可通过构造特制的 Word 文档或 HTML 邮件诱使用户打开，从而在目标系统上执行任意代码，完全控制受影响的系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0354"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 提供的安全公告 MS99-002 对应补丁程序，该补丁可在文档基于含宏的模板启动时弹出安全警告。同时建议在 Word 中将宏安全级别设置为「高」或「禁用所有宏并发出通知」，并避免打开来自不受信任来源的 Office 文档。对于 Outlook，建议禁用预览窗格或使用受保护的视图功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-002"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0024.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1008","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1008.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0873","title":"Sky Communications Skyfull Mail Server MAIL FROM 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Sky Communications Skyfull 1.1.4 邮件服务器在处理 MAIL FROM 命令时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向 SMTP 服务发送超长特制的 MAIL FROM 命令参数触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出，可能造成服务崩溃（拒绝服务）或执行任意代码。该漏洞利用代码已公开，增加了被实际攻击的风险。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0873"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:14.123","remediation":"Skyfull 1.1.4 已停止维护且无官方补丁，建议立即迁移至现代受支持的邮件服务器软件（如 Postfix 3.x 或 Exim 4.x）。若无法立即迁移，应在防火墙层面限制仅受信任 IP 访问 SMTP 服务端口（25/TCP），并部署入侵检测规则监控异常的 MAIL FROM 命令请求以降低被利用风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/759","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19584"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1008.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1013","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1013.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1226","title":"Netscape Communicator 证书密钥远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Netscape Communicator 4.7 及更早版本在处理证书密钥时存在安全漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标用户发送包含超长证书密钥的恶意证书，触发缓冲区溢出，导致浏览器拒绝服务，甚至可能执行任意命令。该漏洞影响范围有限且年代较早，CVSS 评分 2.6，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1226"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-28T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:59.260","remediation":"Netscape Communicator 已于 2002 年停止维护，厂商不再提供安全更新。建议立即停止使用所有 Netscape Communicator 版本，改用 Mozilla Firefox、Google Chrome 或 Microsoft Edge 等仍受支持的现代浏览器。作为临时缓解措施，可在网络边界防火墙或代理服务器上过滤异常长的证书链请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securiteam.com/exploits/Netscape_4_7_and_earlier_vulnerable_to__Huge_Key__DoS.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3436","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/77be9686a381151781bc75b69de578b4d9528aae/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1226.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1226","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1226.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1226.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9jww-v5c9-f3ff/GHSA-9jww-v5c9-f3ff.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1226.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87546/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--5cbad00d-e7aa-4d06-80c2-ba642bb0f45c.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1013.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0713","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0713.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0915","title":"Pacific Software URL Live! 1.0 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Pacific Software URL Live! 1.0 Web 服务器存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送包含 ../（点点斜杠）序列的恶意 HTTP 请求，绕过路径限制读取服务器上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞攻击复杂度低，无需身份认证，影响该软件 1.0 版本。CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0915"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-28T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:19.300","remediation":"升级 Pacific URL Live! 至最新版本（如仍受支持）以修复目录遍历漏洞；该产品已停止维护，建议迁移至 Apache Nginx 等现代 Web 服务器；在网络层面部署 WAF 规则过滤 `../` 及 URL 编码绕过变种作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1129","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/746","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19568"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0713.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0673","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0673.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0882","title":"Falcon Web服务器路径信息泄露漏洞","description":"Falcon Web 服务器存在信息泄露漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向服务器发送超长文件名请求，利用路径处理缺陷确定 Web 根目录的绝对路径。该漏洞源于服务器对畸形文件名的错误处理，导致在错误消息中泄露物理路径信息，可能进一步辅助攻击者规划后续攻击。CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0882"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-28T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:15.210","remediation":"Falcon Web Server 已停止维护，官方不再发布安全更新。建议立即迁移至仍在维护的 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server、Nginx 或 IIS），从根本上消除风险。在迁移完成之前，可在反向代理或 WAF 层面配置规则，过滤或拒绝包含超长文件名的请求（限制 URL 路径长度不超过 2048 字节），作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0882"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0673.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1408","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1408.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0950","title":"Texas Imperial Software WFTPD FTP 服务器远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"WFTPD FTP 服务器存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者通过发送一系列精心构造的 MKD（创建目录）和 CWD（切换目录）命令，创建深层嵌套目录结构触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取目标系统的 root 权限。该漏洞影响 WFTPD 2.34/2.40/3.0 版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0950"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-28","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 WFTPD 至修复版本，在防火墙限制对 21/TCP 端口的访问，仅允许可信 IP 连接；同时禁用匿名 FTP 写入权限，防止攻击者利用 MKD/CWD 命令创建嵌套目录触发溢出。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/747","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19570"],"poc_urls":["https://gitlab.com/exploit-database/exploitdb-bin-sploits/-/raw/main/bin-sploits/19570.tgz"],"exp_urls":["https://gitlab.com/exploit-database/exploitdb-bin-sploits/-/raw/main/bin-sploits/19570.tgz"],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1408.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1017","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1017.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1234","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 LSA 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 的本地安全认证子系统服务 (LSASS.EXE) 存在空指针解引用漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统的 SAM RPC 接口传递空策略句柄调用 SamrOpenDomain、SamrEnumDomainUsers、SamrQueryDomainInfo 等函数，导致 LSASS 进程崩溃，从而引发拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 全版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程触发，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1234"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-26T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:00.263","remediation":"Windows NT 4.0 已终止支持且不再有安全更新，建议立即升级至受支持的 Windows 版本（如 Windows Server 2019/2022）。如无法升级，在防火墙中限制对 RPC（135/TCP、445/TCP）端口的非信任来源访问，并禁用 LSASS 空策略句柄相关的匿名调用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=94096671308565&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3293","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-1234.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1234.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1234","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1234.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1234.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mv63-92x5-p264/GHSA-mv63-92x5-p264.json","https://github.com/uyuni-project/uyuni/blob/df5312ee7a856b9c62fddbe68c2d17d0b5279709/testsuite/features/secondary/min_cve_id_new_syntax.feature","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1234.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87560/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1017.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0922","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0922.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1076","title":"Apple MacOS 9 空闲会话密码保护安全绕过漏洞","description":"MacOS 9 的空闲锁定功能存在安全绕过漏洞。本地攻击者可通过选择\"注销\"选项，在应用程序弹出确认对话框时选择\"取消\"，从而绕过空闲会话的密码保护机制重新进入原本已锁定的会话。该漏洞影响 MacOS 9 系统，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危，需要本地访问权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1076"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-26T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:40.277","remediation":"建议升级到后续受支持版本（Mac OS X 10.0 及以上），因为 Apple 已停止对 Mac OS 9 的支持且不再发布安全补丁。如无法升级，可在系统控制面板中关闭「空闲后需要密码」选项的「退出登录」→「取消」快捷键功能，或通过第三方屏幕锁定软件（如 ASIP Screen Lock）替代系统自带锁定机制，同时加强物理访问控制以防止本地攻击。除管理员外其他用户应设置为普通权限，限制其能够关闭系统进程的能力。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94096348604173&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/745","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1076.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1076","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1076.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1076.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1076.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-54c2-phxc-2hgx/GHSA-54c2-phxc-2hgx.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/745/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1076.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0922.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0702","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0702.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0903","title":"IBM AIX 数据包过滤模块 genfilt 端口过滤绕过漏洞","description":"AIX 操作系统数据包过滤模块中的 genfilt 函数存在端口范围过滤缺陷，当目标端口号大于 32767 时，genfilt 无法正确过滤相关流量。远程攻击者可利用该漏洞通过高端口绕过系统配置的包过滤规则，实现未授权访问，影响 IBM AIX 系统的网络安全策略有效性。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0903"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-26T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:17.797","remediation":"立即安装 IBM APAR IX82821 对应的系统补丁（适用于 AIX 4.3.x/5.x）。如无法安装补丁，应避免在 genfilt 规则中依赖大于 32767 的目标端口进行过滤，改用 AIX IPsec 过滤或第三方防火墙替代 genfilt 实现高端口过滤策略。对于仍在运行的旧版 AIX 系统，建议迁移至受支持的 AIX 7.x 版本并使用原生 iptables 过滤功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0903"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0702.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0672","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0672.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0881","title":"Falcon Web Server 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Falcon Web Server 存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过在 URL 中注入 `../` 等路径穿越序列，突破 Web 根目录限制，读取服务器上任意文件，包括配置文件、密码文件等敏感信息。该漏洞利用难度低，攻击者可批量扫描受影响版本服务器实施数据窃取。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0881"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-26T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:15.097","remediation":"立即停止使用 Falcon Web Server，迁移至 Apache HTTP Server 或 Nginx 等仍在维护的 Web 服务器。如无法立即迁移，应在前置反向代理（如 Nginx）上添加规则过滤请求路径中的连续 \"../\" 序列，同时对 URL 进行归一化解码后再做路径校验，阻止对敏感目录的访问。临时缓解期间仅开放必要 HTTP 端口，并限制 Web 服务的文件根目录权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1127","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/743"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0672.toml"}]